snippet.title: Black Money Hoarders Find Escape Route by Assorting New Currency Sequences

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Black money hoarders find escape route by assorting new currency sequences. Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
